Netizen contribution
Today is the first day of the postgraduate entrance examination. The official website of the Central University for Nationalities postgraduate entrance examination site notified that the first exam should be held before 6:45. I arrived at 6:30 and there were already many classmates. At first we waited in the building, but were later driven out by the security guards to line up. The security guards said that they had not received the notice to enter the examination room at 6:45 and would open the building at 8 o'clock.
Now in the cold wind, some students are reviewing with mobile phone flashlights, and there are coughs in the team.
